{"tha-ap387:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap387:0.2":"Avataphalavagga ","tha-ap387:0.3":"Pharusaphaladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap387:1.1":"“Suvannavannam sambuddham, ","tha-ap387:1.2":"Ahutinam patiggaham; ","tha-ap387:1.3":"Rathiyam patipajjantam, ","tha-ap387:1.4":"Pharusaphalamadasaham. ","tha-ap387:2.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap387:2.2":"yam phalamadadim aham; ","tha-ap387:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap387:2.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap387:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap387:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap387:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap387:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap387:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap387:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap387:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap387:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap387:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap387:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pharusaphaladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap387:7.1":"Pharusaphaladayakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}